<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="Aink147-kilavi">
        cuṟṟattār vēṇṭiya koṭuttut talaimakaṉ varaivu māṭcimaippaṭuttamai yaṟinta tōḻi uvanta vuḷattāḷāyt talaimakaṭkuc colliyatu</p>    <p xml:lang="en">
       Spoken by the confidante  who knew of the fact that the hero had confirmed the marriage, [his] relatives having given him what was wanted, as one with an overjoyed heart, to the heroine.

 </p>
 </div>    
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink147">
<l>ekkar ñāḻaṉ malariṉ makaḷi</l>
<l>roṇṭaḻai yayarun tuṟaivaṉ</l>
<l>ṟaṇṭaḻai vilaiyeṉa nalkiṉa ṉāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
      <l>The man from the ghat in which sweet girls </l>
      <l>Like flowers of Ñāḻal trees in the dunes</l>
       <l> Wear bright leaf[-skirts]</l>
        <l>Gave as the price [= proposal gift] a cool, leaf[-skirt].</l>      
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
